# shadcn/ui Components & Theme

Always use shadcn/ui components for UI elements in the frontend.

## Component Usage

**Use shadcn/ui components** for all UI elements:

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD - Using shadcn components
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader } from "@/components/ui/card"
import { Input } from "@/components/ui/input"

export function MyComponent() {
  return (
    <Card>
      <CardHeader>Title</CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <Input placeholder="Enter text" />
        <Button>Submit</Button>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  )
}

// ❌ BAD - Custom/non-shadcn components
export function MyComponent() {
  return (
    <div className="custom-card">
      <input type="text" />
      <button>Submit</button>
    </div>
  )
}
```

## Theme Consistency

Follow the shadcn theme system using CSS variables and Tailwind utilities:

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD - Using theme variables
<div className="bg-background text-foreground">
  <h1 className="text-primary">Title</h1>
  <p className="text-muted-foreground">Description</p>
</div>

// ❌ BAD - Hardcoded colors
<div className="bg-white text-black">
  <h1 className="text-blue-600">Title</h1>
</div>
```

## Key Theme Colors

- `background` / `foreground` - Main background and text
- `primary` / `primary-foreground` - Primary actions and their text
- `secondary` / `secondary-foreground` - Secondary actions
- `muted` / `muted-foreground` - Muted backgrounds and text
- `accent` / `accent-foreground` - Accent colors
- `destructive` / `destructive-foreground` - Destructive actions
- `border` - Border color
- `input` - Input border color
- `ring` - Focus ring color
